{"tid":1554252,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"9/9交易所要人，柒婆同共狗星期二賀#ChiNazi國慶","createTime":"2019-09-09T01:53:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T01:56:48.000Z","uid":25974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2761c4bc6784fe5df6583d48e5970e36c1b7ba1f","tid":1554252,"uid":25974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:53:27.000Z","msg":"From 我朋友：<br />\n<br />\n「柒婆日日比人屌都無反應，因為佢掛住去salon set頭星期二同金融業一班共狗唱紅歌，賀國慶。<br />\n<br />\n香港金融業就係比呢班共狗把持，我地就去同佢地一幫共狗做冥壽，光復香港。<br />\nPs.佢唔敢比人知自己去到場，名單上只敢寫主嘉賓。<br />\n<br />\n星期二放工後6點港交所集合，不見不散。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0R2Wrsa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0R2Wrsa.jpg&h=19fa18fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36375fdd9668f5b9b87768064187b681d4503bc8","tid":1554252,"uid":25974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:53:43.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"069b44bc9db6cbc24208d91620aeb9ed6a20ad29","tid":1554252,"uid":25974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:53:53.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"fa7b3aeb3139af35eeaf21a2a00892f43952ddd2","tid":1554252,"uid":25974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:54:03.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"56bf87adbcea05c7791b5a4a3cd4d587b937f4de","tid":1554252,"uid":25974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:54:14.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"033973934498188e1df8decaef6363022b0921f0","tid":1554252,"uid":25974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:54:26.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"0854b56b9ebbc1e8a43ac26839e109ce247231c1","tid":1554252,"uid":25974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:54:38.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"3a9837c1cf103d65fae5b5584ef6f4f512ec82fb","tid":1554252,"uid":25974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T01:54:49.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"9215428ec6f3cbce992e06af4a6bb287e37d34f3","tid":1554252,"uid":259